{"text_id":245847,"tokens":["As"," autonomous"," vehicles"," continue"," to"," gain"," popularity",","," it"," is"," essential"," to"," weigh"," the"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," this"," emerging"," technology","."," On"," one"," hand",","," autonomous"," vehicles"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," the"," way"," we"," travel",","," promising"," to"," reduce"," traffic"," accidents",","," promote"," sustainability",","," and"," make"," our"," roads"," safer","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," the"," rise"," of"," autonomous"," vehicles"," poses"," significant"," economic"," and"," social"," concerns"," that"," cannot"," be"," ignored",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," pressing"," concerns"," surrounding"," autonomous"," vehicles"," is"," their"," potential"," impact"," on"," low","-","income"," workers"," who"," rely"," on"," driving"," for"," a"," living","."," Taxi"," drivers",","," ride","-","share"," drivers",","," and"," delivery"," personnel"," all"," stand"," to"," lose"," their"," jobs"," as"," autonomous"," vehicles"," take"," over","."," While"," proponents"," of"," autonomous"," vehicles"," argue"," that"," these"," jobs"," will"," simply"," be"," retra","ined"," to"," accommodate"," the"," changing"," landscape",","," it"," is"," unclear"," whether"," this"," retraining"," will"," be"," sufficient"," to"," support"," the"," millions"," of"," workers"," affected","."," Moreover",","," the"," loss"," of"," these"," jobs"," will"," disproportion","ately"," affect"," low","-","income"," communities",","," exacerb","ating"," existing"," economic"," inequalities",".","\n\n","However",","," autonomous"," vehicles"," do"," promise"," to"," reduce"," accidents"," caused"," by"," human"," error",","," including"," drunk"," driving"," and"," reckless"," behavior","."," According"," to"," the"," National"," Highway"," Traffic"," Safety"," Administration",","," approximately"," ","9","4","%"," of"," accidents"," are"," caused"," by"," human"," error","."," Autonomous"," vehicles",","," by"," virtue"," of"," their"," programming"," and"," sensors",","," are"," designed"," to"," eliminate"," human"," oversight",","," significantly"," reducing"," the"," risk"," of"," accidents","."," Furthermore",","," autonomous"," vehicles"," can"," also"," reduce"," traffic"," congestion"," and"," promote"," more"," efficient"," transportation"," networks",","," reducing"," travel"," times"," and"," increasing"," productivity",".","\n\n","While"," autonomous"," vehicles"," do"," offer"," some"," advantages",","," there"," are"," also"," significant"," safety"," concerns"," to"," consider","."," For"," instance",","," the"," reliance"," on"," complex"," software"," and"," hardware"," raises"," concerns"," about"," system"," failure"," and"," hacking","."," Moreover",","," the"," need"," for"," a"," trained"," and"," attentive"," driver"," to"," take"," control"," of"," the"," vehicle"," in"," emergency"," situations"," raises"," concerns"," about"," the"," practicality"," of"," autonomous"," vehicles",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," autonomous"," vehicles"," hold"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," the"," way"," we"," travel",","," the"," economic"," and"," social"," impacts"," must"," be"," carefully"," considered","."," While"," the"," promise"," of"," reduced"," accidents"," and"," congestion"," is"," enticing",","," the"," potential"," loss"," of"," jobs"," and"," economic"," disruption"," must"," be"," addressed","."," As"," we"," move"," forward"," with"," the"," development"," of"," autonomous"," vehicles",","," it"," is"," crucial"," that"," policymakers"," and"," industry"," leaders"," prioritize"," the"," welfare"," of"," low","-","income"," workers"," and"," ensure"," a"," smooth"," transition"," to"," this"," new"," technological"," landscape","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}